# 🔹 Basic Operations

---

## 1️⃣ Enqueue

Insertion at Rear.

```text
10 20

Enqueue(30)

10 20 30
```

Time Complexity:

[
O(1)
]

---

## 2️⃣ Dequeue

Deletion from Front.

```text
10 20 30

Dequeue()

20 30
```

Time Complexity:

[
O(1)
]

---

## 3️⃣ Front()

Returns first element.

---

## 4️⃣ Rear()

Returns last element.

---

## 5️⃣ isEmpty()

Checks whether queue is empty.

---

## 6️⃣ isFull()

Checks overflow condition.

