# 🔹 Common GATE Traps

### Trap 1

Queue follows:

✅ FIFO

NOT LIFO.

---

### Trap 2

Circular queue full condition:

[
(rear+1)%n=front
]

---

### Trap 3

Priority queue does NOT necessarily follow FIFO.

---

### Trap 4

Deque allows operations at both ends.

